ptain lieutenant]]/[[Lieutenant (navy)|lieutenant]]) \u2013 1 June 1939{{sfn|Busch|R\u00f6ll|2003|p=42}}\n*''[[Korvettenkapit\u00e4n]]'' ([[corvette captain]]/[[lieutenant commander]]) \u2013 19 March 1941, effective as of 1 March 1941{{sfn|Busch|R\u00f6ll|2003|p=42}}\n*''[[Fregattenkapit\u00e4n]]'' ([[frigate captain]]/[[commander]]) \u2013 1 September 1944{{sfn|Busch|R\u00f6ll|2003|p=42}}\n\n====Bundesmarine====\n*''[[Fregattenkapit\u00e4n]]'' (frigate captain/commander) \u2013 1 December 1955\n*''[[Kapit\u00e4n zur See]]'' ([[captain at sea]]/[[Captain (naval)|captain]]) \u2013 12 December 1958{{sfn|Busch|R\u00f6ll|2003|p=43}}\n*''[[Flotilla admiral|Flottillenadmiral]]'' ([[flotilla admiral]]/[[Commodore (rank)|commodore]]<!--Rear Admiral?-->) on probation \u2013 1 June 1965{{sfn|Busch|R\u00f6ll|2003|p=43}}\n*''Flottillenadmiral'' (flotilla admiral/commodore) \u2013 15 December 1965{{sfn|Busch|R\u00f6ll|2003|p=43}}\n\n==Translation notes==\n{{Reflist|group=\"Tr\"|30em}}\n\n==Notes==\n{{Reflist|group=\"Note\"}}\n\n==References==\n\n===Citations===\n{{Reflist|25em}}\n\n===Bibliography===\n{{Refbegin|30em}}\n* {{cite book\n  |last=Blair\n  |first=Clay\n  |authorlink=Clay Blair\n  |title=Hitler's U-Boat War: The Hunters, 1939\u20131942\n  |publisher=Random House\n  |year=1998\n  |isbn=978-0-30787-437-5\n  |ref=harv\n}}\n* {{Cite book\n  |last1=Busch\n  |first1=Rainer\n  |last2=R\u00f6ll\n  |first2=Hans-Joachim\n  |year=2003\n  |title=Der U-Boot-Krieg 1939\u20131945 \u2014 Die Ritterkreuztr\u00e4ger der U-Boot-Waffe von September 1939 bis Mai 1945\n  |trans-title=The U-Boat War 1939\u20131945 \u2014 The Knight's Cross Bearers of the U-Boat Force from September 1939 to May 1945\n  |language=German\n  |location=Hamburg, Berlin, Bonn Germany\n  |publisher=Verlag E.S. Mittler & Sohn\n  |isbn=978-3-8132-0515-2\n  |ref=harv\n}}\n* {{cite book\n  |last=Claasen\n  |first=Adam R. A.\n  |year=2001\n  |title=Hitler's Northern War: The Luftwaffe's Ill-Fated Campaign, 1940\u201319