999|p=46}}\n|-\n|align=\"right\"|16 March 1941\n|align=\"left\" |''U-99''\n|align=\"left\" |''[[list of shipwrecks in March 1941#16 March|Ferm]]''\n|align=\"left\" |{{flag|Norway}}\n|align=\"right\"|6,593\n|align=\"left\" |Sunk\n|align=\"left\" |{{sfn|Rohwer|1999|p=46}}\n|-\n|align=\"right\"|16 March 1941\n|align=\"left\" |''U-99''\n|align=\"left\" |''[[list of shipwrecks in March 1941#16 March|Franche-Comt\u00e9]]''\n|align=\"left\" |{{flag|United Kingdom|civil}}\n|align=\"right\"|9,314\n|align=\"left\" |Damaged\n|align=\"left\" |{{sfn|Rohwer|1999|p=46}}\n|-\n|align=\"right\"|16 March 1941\n|align=\"left\" |''U-99''\n|align=\"left\" |''[[list of shipwrecks in March 1941#16 March|J. B. White]]''\n|align=\"left\" |{{flag|Canada|1921}}\n|align=\"right\"|7,375\n|align=\"left\" |Sunk\n|align=\"left\" |{{sfn|Rohwer|1999|p=46}}\n|-\n|align=\"right\"|16 March 1941\n|align=\"left\" |''U-99''\n|align=\"left\" |''[[list of shipwrecks in March 1941#16 March|Korshamn]]''\n|align=\"left\" |{{flag|Sweden}}\n|align=\"right\"|6,673\n|align=\"left\" |Sunk\n|align=\"left\" |{{sfn|Rohwer|1999|p=46}}\n|-\n|align=\"right\"|16 March 1941\n|align=\"left\" |''U-99''\n|align=\"left\" |''[[list of shipwrecks in March 1941#16 March|Venetia]]''\n|align=\"left\" |{{flag|United Kingdom|civil}}\n|align=\"right\"|5,728\n|align=\"left\" |Sunk\n|align=\"left\" |{{sfn|Rohwer|1999|p=46}}\n|}\n\n===Awards===\n* [[Wehrmacht Long Service Award]] 4th Class (2 October 1936){{sfn|Busch|R\u00f6ll|2003|p=42}}\n* [[Memel Medal]] (26 October 1939){{sfn|Busch|R\u00f6ll|2003|p=42}}\n* [[Iron Cross]] (1939)\n** 2nd Class (17 October 1939){{sfn|Busch|R\u00f6ll|2003|p=42}}{{sfn|Thomas|1997|p=406}}\n** 1st Class (17 December 1939){{sfn|Busch|R\u00f6ll|2003|p=42}}{{sfn|Thomas|1997|p=406}}\n* [[U-boat War Badge]] (1939) (9 November 1939){{sfn|Busch|R\u00f6ll|2003|p=42}}\n* [[Sudetenland Medal]] (20 December 1939){{sfn|Busch|R\u00f6ll|2003|p=42}}\n* [[Knight's Cross of the Iron Cross with Oak Leaves and Swords]]\n** Kni