on Cross with Oak Leaves and Swords]]\n[[Category:Bundesmarine admirals]]\n[[Category:German prisoners of war in World War II]]\n[[Category:Reichsmarine personnel]]\n[[Category:Burials at sea]]\n[[Category:Flotilla admirals of the German Navy]]\n", "name_user": "XAM2175", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200ePrisoner of war:typo", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Otto_Kretschmer"}
